WHATWG Encoding Standard

This package includes behavior and compact data derived from the WHATWG Encoding Standard for encoding labels, web-compatible label remapping, TextDecoder compatibility expectations, and legacy single-byte encoding indexes used by the native decoder tables.

Covered materials in this package include support data or behavior for `windows-1251`, `windows-1252`, `iso-8859-5`, `koi8-r`, `IBM866`/`cp866`, and the web-compatible remapping of labels such as `iso-8859-1`, `latin1`, `us-ascii`, and related aliases to `windows-1252`.

Source: https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/
Repository data: https://github.com/whatwg/encoding
