Unicode Standard and Unicode data

This package includes behavior and compact data derived from Unicode materials for UTF-8 and UTF-16 handling, scalar value and surrogate rules, BOM-related behavior, Unicode code point assignments used in encoding maps, and replacement character semantics.

Source: https://www.unicode.org/
